## Errors & Mistakes
- I assumed test_flask_server was backend-agnostic and un-gated it; it FAILED on
  the fake: httpcore.RemoteProtocolError 'Server disconnected without sending a
  response' + a SystemExit:1 thread exception. Root cause: the flask route calls
  weave.publish() inside a werkzeug request thread, where the in-process fake
  client is not reachable. A served backend (CH in tests) doesn't have this. So
  it's an architectural limit, not a missing fake capability -> NOT_CLICKHOUSE_BACKEND.

